Most of the app improvements this week will help you find songs faster!

What’s New:
•    Browsing songs & artists just got easier with continuous scrolling.
•    Tap the Widget titles & get a list view.
•    Know what’s always “Hot at Venue” from the main screen.
•    General bug fixes & performance improvements.

Here’s why you should download this app update:

- We will let you know when there is little to no wait time to play your music on the jukebox. Make sure you’re opted into notifications to receive our alerts!
- Search just got better! Misspelled a song or an artist name? No worries! The app will always show the last set of results instead of showing nothing.
- You asked, we listened! You know those messages that would pop up after you play a song? We changed it up and made it so they don’t appear as often. Keep the feedback rolling in!
